<br>
Someone asks for a rez : 2 solutions. I can rez him and i do it OR i can't rez him and i don't do it. Simple. You can offer 20kpp if you want, i won't do it if i can't. Offering insane amount of money dwon't change my mind, i won't drop a group to do it, i won't cross several zones to do it if i don't want to. When i say &quot;i can't, sorry&quot;, this is not your business why i can't.<br>
<br>
People have to expect a &quot;no&quot; sometimes. Nothing to do with pps, at least for me. Don't get mad if i say &quot;no&quot;. I'll never pester a rogue or a tpers if they say no.<br>
<br>
I'm not a cruel cleric thou, i rezz freely a lot and i never ask for a donation. Rezzed people give whatever they want :-)<br>
